  "detailed_description": "beVaiR is a unique combination of story and immersive VR strategy game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/17b68802d86959231b4927383c74d5ea.poster.avif?t=1677312758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/17b68802d86959231b4927383c74d5ea.webm?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/17b68802d86959231b4927383c74d5ea.mp4?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Immerse yourself in a dystopian future, join a faction and help it dominate by collecting, modifying and shooting energy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/44d376cc2606bf9553c080aa1dd919dd.poster.avif?t=1677312758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/44d376cc2606bf9553c080aa1dd919dd.webm?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/44d376cc2606bf9553c080aa1dd919dd.mp4?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Create new nodes and manipulate the neural network surrounding you. Find a way to influence the AI and pry all secretes out of it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/89a934d7ff54adce200959c3431d9f9f.poster.avif?t=1677312758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/89a934d7ff54adce200959c3431d9f9f.webm?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/89a934d7ff54adce200959c3431d9f9f.mp4?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Prevent the network from being sabotaged or take advantage of it. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/d6daebbf26803e1cbd44119925f845ee.poster.avif?t=1677312758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/d6daebbf26803e1cbd44119925f845ee.webm?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/d6daebbf26803e1cbd44119925f845ee.mp4?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Choose your favorite playlist and let the network respond to songs from your local music library.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/70537d1d1d3d71d161734b8b2f24b766.poster.avif?t=1677312758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/70537d1d1d3d71d161734b8b2f24b766.webm?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/70537d1d1d3d71d161734b8b2f24b766.mp4?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Unveil the puzzle by uncovering the entire story of lies and intrigue.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/633837351f4b5039489142343ff3a3fa.poster.avif?t=1677312758\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/633837351f4b5039489142343ff3a3fa.webm?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711940/extras/633837351f4b5039489142343ff3a3fa.mp4?t=1677312758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Be strategic. beVaiR.",
